Package: inventory
Type: Package
Title: Computation of Optimal Inventory Reorder Points
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(c('Dennis', 'L.'), 'Malandro',
    email = 'dennismalandro@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: Fit nonparametric density estimates to lead-time and
    demand data.  Integrate those "conditonal" densities to get a
    the marginal lead-time demand distribution.  This in turn is 
    integrated to get the optimal reorder point, for a given
    service level.
